column2: Tell me the latest travel and leisure news.
column6: The latest travel and leisure news includes a lightweight travel wallet on sale at Amazon, a trip through Navajo Nation, highlights of Osaka's food scene, and information on Vancouver Art Gallery. Other news includes uncrowded public beaches in Dubai, beaches to visit in St. Augustine, a fall travel sale on nonstop flights, fire danger in Yellowstone National Park, and a comfortable and supportive hiking sandal on sale at Amazon. There's also a comment on the importance of travel for relationships and mental health according to a source interviewed by Travel + Leisure.

Provider: Travel + Leisure

Provider: Travel + Leisure

Description: As Western Canada’s largest public art museum, the Vancouver Art Gallery is a top attraction for art enthusiasts. Browse the works of Emily Carr, British Columbia’s beloved painter, and explore the blockbuster international shows and contemporary collections found throughout the three-story historic space.
Provider: Travel + Leisure
Date Published: 2023-07-25T20:27:00.0000000Z

Description: “Dubai has some great and uncrowded public beaches, where you can just enjoy the warm Arabian sea and sunshine at no cost,” says Sullivan. Try Kite Beach, since it also offers fantastic showers and bathrooms, plus a handful of food stands and coffee shops. For an extra treat, rent a Careem bike and cruise along Kite Beach’s lengthy boardwalk.
Provider: Travel + Leisure
Date Published: 2023-07-25T18:05:00.0000000Z

Description: While the main appeal of St. Augustine is certainly its winding cobblestone streets and centuries-old Spanish colonial architecture, its beaches are also worth a visit. Nearby St. Augustine Beach is a popular choice, while the white sands of tranquil Crescent Beach and breezy Butler Beach are perfect places to unwind.
Provider: Travel + Leisure
Date Published: 2023-07-25T17:29:00.0000000Z

Description: The “ Get the Fall Rolling” sale, which must be booked by 11:59 p.m. ET on July 26, is valid on nonstop flights from Sept. 6 through Nov. 15 except on Fridays and Sundays, the airline shared with Travel + Leisure. To book, travelers must use the promo code “FALLTRAVEL” and spend at least $50 per flight segment (excluding the taxes and fees).
Provider: Travel + Leisure
Date Published: 2023-07-25T15:56:00.0000000Z

Description: The fire danger level for Yellowstone National Park has been upgraded to “high” after a wildland fire was spotted in the park for the first time this year.
Provider: Travel + Leisure
Date Published: 2023-07-25T17:38:00.0000000Z

Description: The Dream Pairs Men’s Hiking Sandals are supportive, breathable, and incredibly comfortable for hiking, walking tours, and sightseeing adventures. Grab these quick-drying sandals while they’re 28 percent off at Amazon.
Provider: Travel + Leisure
Date Published: 2023-07-25T13:29:00.0000000Z

Description: What’s great about travel is that it allows you to have experiences and make memories with those you love, “both of which are important to the bonding and sustaining of relationships,” Saltz told T+L. Saltz added that “strong, trusted, long-lasting relationships are important for general happiness, well-being, and mental health.”
Provider: Travel + Leisure
Date Published: 2023-07-25T11:52:00.0000000Z
